title: Nondegeneracy of the entire solution for the $N$-Laplace Liouville equation. (arXiv:2210.16757v2 [math.AP] UPDATED)
description: In this note, we prove the nondegenracy of the explicit finite-mass solution to the $N$-Laplace Liouville equation on the whole space, which is recently shown to be unique up to scaling and translation.
dc:creator: Futoshi Takahashi
